(41, 12, 11, 19, 118, 23, 23, NULL, 'Connection of Marvelous Deeds', 'Both passages emphasize the phrase, ''This is the Lord''s doing; it is marvellous in our eyes.'' This connection highlights the significance of God''s actions being recognized as marvelous.', 'quotation', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 12, 11, 35, 1, 5, 5, 'marvellous in our eyes', 'Marvelous Works of the Lord', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of marveling at God''s works. Mark 12:11 reflects on the Lord''s marvelous actions, while Habakkuk 1:5 invites people to wonder at the extraordinary work God will perform.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 12, 11, 44, 2, 32, 36, 'this was the Lord’s doing', 'Marvelous Works of God', 'Both passages emphasize the divine action of God in raising Jesus and the marvel associated with it. The phrase ''marvellous in our eyes'' in Mark resonates with the acknowledgment of God''s power in Acts, where the resurrection of Jesus is presented as a significant and wondrous event.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 12, 11, 44, 3, 12, 16, 'marvellous in our eyes', 'Marvelous Works of God', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine action and the response of the people. Both passages emphasize the marvel of God''s works, with Mark 12:11 stating it is ''marvellous in our eyes'' and Acts 3:12 questioning why the people marvel at the healing.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 12, 11, 4, 23, 23, 23, 'this was the Lord’s doing', 'Divine Action and Marvelous Works', 'Both passages emphasize the marvelous works of God and His protection over His people. The phrase ''What hath God wrought!'' in Numbers resonates with the Lord''s doing in Mark, highlighting divine intervention.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 12, 11, 49, 3, 8, 11, 'marvellous in our eyes', 'Marvelous Works of God', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s marvelous works and wisdom. Both passages emphasize the extraordinary nature of God''s plans and purposes, showcasing His grace and the revelation of mysteries through Christ.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 12, 11, 51, 1, 27, 27, 'marvellous in our eyes', 'Divine Marvel and Hope', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s marvelous work in revealing Christ, which is described as a mystery. Both passages emphasize the extraordinary nature of God''s actions and the hope found in Christ.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
